title.rendered: HSP TailAssist Dual Action Tail Gate Strut – VW Amarok 2011+

content.rendered:
HSP TailAssist Dual Action Tail Gate Strut – VW Amarok 2011+ (Dampening and Weight Reduction)

The Tail Gate Assist is a fantastic addition to a vehicles tailgate. Using a two-way strut system that dampens the weight while the tailgate is declining and reduces the weight when inclining. Utilising factory mounting points makes the installation a breeze as there is no need to remove the tailgate.

– Dampens weight of the tailgate when declining.

– Reduces weight when inclining.

– Twin strut system.

– Non-Intrusive design.
